Abstract = {{Reclaimed mining-induced subsidence area soils (RMSs) could restore soil
   quality and crop productivity in coal mining area. This study was
   conducted to evaluate the effects of mineral-processing wastes (fly ash
   vs coal gangue) as backfill substrates on soil chemical and microbial
