   0.42; Cu = 213 mg.kg(-1), Backslope - Ph = 7.59; Cox= 1.33 \%; BD = 1.36
   g.cm(3); POR = 49.30 \%; K = 0.46; Cu = 194 mg.kg(-1), Footslope - Ph =
   7.60; Cox= 1.34 \%; BD = 1.26 g.cm(3); POR = 52.30 \%; K = 0.39; Cu =
   215 mg.kg(-1). In case of ploughed vineyard parameters reached values
   of: summit Ph = 7.72; Cox= 1.76 \%; BD = 1.50 g.cm(3); POR = 43.10 \%; K
   = 0.36; Cu = 188 mg.kg(-1), backslope - Ph = 7.42; Cox= 1.08 \%; BD =
   1.38 g.cm(3); POR = 48.20 \%; K = 0.48; Cu = 124 mg.kg(-1), footslope -
