   = 144 mg.kg(-1).The higher variability of soil properties and more
   intensive transformation of soil profile related to more accelerated
   erosion processes on ploughed vineyard have been noticed. Values of pH,
   organic carbon content and Cu content were considerable lower in the
   eroded part of the ploughed vineyard if compared with the slightly
